{
    "version": "1.1.4",
    "description": "Viap - 专业的 Windows 应用存储重定向工具，使用符号链接将 C 盘应用无损迁移到其他磁盘",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/Chunyu33/viap",
    "license": "MIT",
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://github.com/Chunyu33/viap/releases/download/v1.1.4/viap_1.1.4_x64-setup.exe",
            "hash": "36583785ed4f90ae29f597f43ed4eae9bf5b35546c47c29debbe0728de0c45db"
        }
    },
    "depends": "7zip",
    "installer": {
        "script": [
            "& 7z x \"$dir\\$fname\" -o\"$dir\" -y | Out-Null",
            "Remove-Item \"$dir\\$fname\" -Force",
            "Remove-Item \"$dir\\`$PLUGINSDIR\" -Recurse -Force"
        ]
    },
    "bin": "viap.exe",
    "shortcuts": [
        [
            "viap.exe",
            "Viap"
        ]
    ],
    "checkver": {
        "github": "Chunyu33/viap"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "architecture": {
            "64bit": {
                "url": "https://github.com/Chunyu33/viap/releases/download/v$version/viap_$version_x64-setup.exe"
            }
        }
    },
    "notes": [
        "Viap 是一款 Tauri 桌面应用，可将 C 盘应用通过符号链接无损迁移到其他磁盘",
        "运行方式: viap 或在开始菜单搜索 'Viap'",
        "",
        "功能特性:",
        "- 一键迁移 C 盘应用到其他磁盘",
        "- 一键恢复，随时迁回原位置",
        "- 智能识别开发者目录（Gradle、Maven、npm/Yarn、Cargo、pip/uv、NuGet、Claude Code、Codex 等）",
        "",
        "注意: 该工具需要管理员权限运行以创建符号链接"
    ]
}
